<br>
POP3 (Incoming) Mail Server<br>
A personal POP3 mail server enables you to receive mail on your domain at mail.yourdomain.ext.<br>
<br>
SMTP (Outgoing) Mail Server<br>
A personal SMTP mail server enables you to send mail out through your domain at mail.yourdomain.ext.<br>
<br>
Internet Message Access Protocol<br>
An Internet e-mail protocol which allows access of your e-mail from any IMAP compatible application. Your mail resides on the server level while working with it, versus POP mail which is downloaded from the server into your mail program.<br>
<br>
Horde WebMail<br>
