<br>
Countdown<br>
You can create a countdown box to countdown to a specified date.<br>
<br>
CGI Email<br>
CGI Email can make nicely formatted forms output in email that has been submitted over the web.<br>
<br>
FormMail Clone<br>
FormMail-clone is a clone of Matt Wrights FormMail.<br>
<br>
Entropy Search<br>
This script enables a nice, quick search engine that can help your visitors find information that they are interested in more easily.<br>
<br>
Entropy Banner<br>
This feature allows you to create rotating banner ads.<br>
<br>
