Weekly Server Backups<br>
The process of copying files on a weekly basis so that they are preserved in case of catastrophic equipment failure. If files are damaged on the server, we resort to the backup copy to restore the files back to the machine.<br>
<br>
Network Connectivity<br>
Our servers are connected to diverse Internet backbones with a total bandwidth capacity of 400 MBPS.<br>
